author: cbc
title: Corner Brook teen missing for more than a day
text:
Police are seraching for 16-year-old Kailee Nardini. (Royal Newfoundland Constabulary)
A 16-year-old has been missing from Raymond Heights area of Corner Brook since Monday morning, police say.
The Royal Newfoundland Constabulary in Corner Brook is looking for Kailee Nardini, a teenager who was reported missing at about 11:40 a.m. Monday.
Police say Nardini is 5-foot-4, 135 pounds with green eyes and long brown hair. She was last seen wearing a red hoodie, black leggings, fur-topped boots and a green army coat.
She also wears glasses.
Police are asking anyone with information about the girl to contact them.
